                    <description>&lt;p&gt;obdfilter-survey test_3a PASS :&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/sub_tests/f0f3da80-0b9d-11e8-a6ad-52540065bddc&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/sub_tests/f0f3da80-0b9d-11e8-a6ad-52540065bddc&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
